node.text:
For all of us that stopped while packing Yumbox for our child & asked ourselves why I can’t get nice packed lunches like this - full of variety and color. Yes, you can get your own Yumbox. We all deserve one 🙃

Repost @candishes.kitchen
・・・
Mom confession, while I love making cute bentos and snacks for my kids, I always forget to make myself something when we go on outings! Every.single.time! Who’s with me? It goes to show that momma’s always put their kids first above anything else! But we always need to remember to feed ourselves too! It’s so important! Mom tip: get yourself a bento box and while you’re making your kids one, you have no more excuses to forget about yourself anymore because you have one too! 

Today I’m sharing my own snacking bento box for my 12 hr shift! I’d like to call this my charcuterie style bento: 

☀️ granola bear
☀️ cherries
☀️ strawberries
☀️ bison salami
☀️ balsamic vinegar triscuits and cheese
☀️ kalamata olives 
☀️ mixed nuts and fruit

We are proud to work with so many small businesses worldwide. Times are hard, but by supporting each other we will get to the other side stronger than ever. ✨

node.text:
So many great lunch packing ideas by @lunches_by_lindsay
・・・
Tired of the same old lunches? 🙋🏼‍♀️
Feeling stuck for ideas? 🤷🏼‍♀️
Worried about the upcoming school year? 🤦🏼‍♀️

Today I'm sharing with you:
🎉OUR TOP NINE SIMPLE LUNCHES🎉
voted by my kids, to help you when you're feeling the lunch-packing struggle.

All of these lunches have been packed in our Yumbox Original or Yumbox Panino ~ perfect bento boxes for your littles who are just starting school, or kiddos that love variety.

Here are my kids top nine favourite lunches (from top left to bottom right)

1️⃣ Cold pasta & veggie salad
2️⃣ Cheese quesadillas
3️⃣ Hard boiled eggs
4️⃣ Tuna salad with crackers
5️⃣ Turkey and cheese wraps
6️⃣ Chickpeas with tortilla roll ups
7️⃣ Mini bagels with cream cheese
8️⃣ French toast skewers
9️⃣ Waffled pizza

Like these lunch ideas? Make sure to ⭐SAVE⭐ this post so you can refer back easily throughout the year (just click on the flag-shaped pentagon in the bottom right, below the picture).

❓ Have questions about any of the lunches?  Ask away!
.
